snippet.title: Fall Guys Season 3 - Official Trailer | Game Awards 2020
snippet.description:
Check out the trailer for Fall Guys Season 3. The winter themed update with 7 new levels, 30+ new skins and new obstacles. Coming to PS5 and PC on December 15.

#ign #thegameawards2020 #gaming
